{
  "description": "A nighttime view of a pier with several small buildings and a large bridge spanning overhead. The bridge is adorned with strings of lights that create a bright, linear pattern against the dark sky.  A sign reading \"Red's JAVA\" is prominently displayed on a small, brightly lit building with red and white trim. Other buildings along the pier are similarly lit, some with signs indicating businesses. There is a walkway with a pedestrian crossing. A few people are visible walking along the pier. The overall scene has a slightly worn, but festive atmosphere, suggestive of a lively waterfront area.",
